data.description: This beautiful 2-story Challenger Home located in Woodmen Hills West is 3 Bed, 3 Bath with an attached fully finished 2-car garage. Upon Entry you are welcomed by luxury vinyl planking with an Office on the main accompanied by French door entry. The Family room of this home has carpet throughout with a Ceiling fan, Windows that offer natural lighting and window coverings included (blinds). The Kitchen is a highlighted feature offering Granite counters, all stainless steel appliances, 5 burner Gas range and built-in microwave with a spacious pantry and dining room combination. Mechanical room has Goodman furnace and Hydro jet 50 gallon water heater and Central Air cooling. Lastly, with a fully fenced backyard and sprinkler system fully landscaped w/grass and bordering rocks. Garage fridge, washer and dryer does not convey.
